---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css"
import image from "../assets/image.png";
import image2 from "../assets/github-mark-white.svg";
---
<Layout title="Sobre Mí">
    <html>

<div class = "about-container">
    <section class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between p-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center md:text-left">
        <!-- Texto más a la izquierda -->
        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:-ml-27"> <!-- Movemos el texto más a la izquierda -->
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-white font-sans">Christian Lara</h2>
            <p class="text-orange-400 text-2xl mt-2">@Full Stack Developer</p>
            <p class="text-base mt-4 text-gray-100 md:w-full text-justify leading-relaxed"></p>
                Apasionado por el desarrollo web y la tecnología, creando experiencias digitales atractivas y funcionales.
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Modi voluptatibus voluptatum iste animi molestiae consequuntur, inventore qui, exercitationem, ut eaque tenetur.
                Quidem accusamus atque vel quaerat laudantium error, dignissimos earum.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
                <a href="#" class="border-2 border-orange-500 px-2 py-2 rounded-lg text-pink-400 hover:bg-pink-500 hover:text-white transition"><img src={image2.src} /></a>
                <a href="#" class="border-2 border-pink-500 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-pink-400 hover:bg-pink-500 hover:text-white transition">LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="#" class="border-5 border-pink-500 px-2 py-2 rounded-lg text-pink-400 hover:bg-pink-500 hover:text-white transition">Email</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Imagen más a la derecha -->
        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex justify-center md:justify-end md:ml-25"> <!-- Movemos la imagen más a la derecha -->
            <img src={image.src} alt="Foto de perfil" class="w-80 h-80 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-lg" />
        </div>
    </section>
    
    
<style>
    .about-container {
        background-color: black;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
    }

</style>

</body>
</html>

</Layout>
